metadata.name: Lombok Kidz #1
metadata.description:
Lombok Kidz, powered by the Open Town project, is a generative NFT collection of 10000 art pieces, from which 100 units are included in a 1st series being sold.

Open Town is an experimental project to plan and co-create autonomous cities around the world with the power of community and the crypto world.

Created by the Indonesian artists Dany Saputra, Lombok Kidz represent Lombok's future children enjoying opportunities to improve their English skills towards a bright future.
metadata.creator: Dany Saputra
